Pilot project. For testing only!

Fast & simple cart interface for OpenCart

Installation:

1) Copy files into the root category of your store;
2) Replace default javascript methods in the file catalog/view/javascript/common.js (see catalog/view/javascript/common_patch.js)
3) Modify the template files to remove unnecessary items
4) Install and activate OCU Cart module in administrative panel
5) Enjoy and report to this page: https://github.com/shaman/opencart-cart/issues

Ukrainian support:
http://forum.opencart.ua/viewtopic.php?f=5&t=533

